  <h>compound adjectives</h>

  <section>
    <h>noun-adjective compounds</h>
    <p>Examples from H. Cameron Gillies (1902) <emph>The Elements of Gaelic Grammar</emph> td. 62 – <ul>
        <li><g>bàrr-bhuidhe</g>
          <en>yellow-topped</en> – </li>
        <li><g>tonn-gheal</g>
          <en>white-waved</en> – <ul>
            <li>masculine <ul>
                <li>nominative – (an) cuan <g>tonn-gheal</g>
                  <en>a/the white-waved ocean</en></li>
                <li>dative – <ul>
                    <li>air cuan <g>tonn-gheal</g>
                      <en>on a white-waved ocean</en></li>
                    <li>air a’ chuan <g>thonn-gheal</g>
                      <en>on the white-waved ocean</en></li>
                  </ul></li>
                <li>genitive – <ul>
                    <li>dath cuain <g><m>thuinn</m>-ghil</g>
                      <en>colour of a white-waved ocean</en></li>
                    <li>dath a’ chuain <g>thuinn-ghil</g>
                      <en>the colour of the white-waved ocean</en></li>
                  </ul></li>
              </ul>
            </li>
            <li>feminine <ul>
                <li>nominative – <ul>
                    <li>fairge <g>thonn-gheal</g>
                      <en>a white-waved sea</en></li>
                    <li>an fhairge <g>thonn-gheal</g>
                      <en>the white-waved sea</en></li>
                  </ul></li>
                <li>dative – <ul>
                    <li>air fairge <g><m>thuinn</m>-ghil</g>
                      <en>on a white-waved sea</en></li>
                    <li>air an fhairge <g>thuinn-ghil</g>
                      <en>on the white-waved sea</en></li>
                  </ul></li>
                <li>genitive – dath (na) fairge <g><m>thuinn(e)</m>-ghile</g>
                  <en>(the) colour of a/the white-waved sea</en></li>
              </ul>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </p>
  </section>


  <section>
    <h>adjective-adjective compounds</h>
    <p><g>mìn-bhreac</g>
      <en>fine-spotted</en></p>
    <p><g>ciuin-gheal</g>
      <en>calm-white</en></p>
  </section>

